features: 📚 Gifts for Book Lovers : Solid wood small bookshelf makes a decorative and functional book gift. It makes a great gift for Mother's Day, Father's Day, bookmarks for men and women, librarians, book clubs. Bookshelf can be used as a book display shelf, or there is space in the middle to place reading glasses or other items used for books.

📚 Books Plants Desktop Decor : With its black open book print, plants, and the words “Just One More Chapter,” Inspiring and sophisticated design further enhances the uniqueness of the bookcase, this coffee book shelf is a memorable piece your book-loving mom, sister, aunt, friend, or coworker.

📚 Elegant and Beautiful : Our triangular bookshelf is made of high quality solid wood, Measures approximately 11.8" x 7.1" x 6.1" (30 x 18.2 x 15.7cm), with 4" diameter coffee cup base and 0.4" pen holder. Perfect size to open your book without taking up too much space, allowing you to read with pleasure.

📚 Home and Office Bookshelf : Your bookmark features a smooth surface and wood grain color to match many home or office décor. It eliminates creased spines, paper bookmarks or folded corners and when you're not using it, just slide it into your book and it becomes a bookmark, holding your place until you're ready to continue reading. Your favorite book can be proudly displayed in your lounge, bedroom or study.

📚 Kind Tips : Bookshelves are carefully handcrafted, the final tone and wood grain may vary slightly from one bookcase to another.Don’t worry, since the bed reading bookshelf is made of natural wood, every piece of wood is unique. The bottom of the bookshelf is equipped with 4 anti-slip pads, allowing you to place it easily no matter where you place it.
body.description: Gifts for Book LoversIt’s a bit difficult to convince your bookaholic friend to put down her paperback or save the next chapter for another day, Their love for printed pages is unconditional. Thus, if you want to grab their attention, especially on their special day, get them something that goes well with books.That something can be a small bookshelf like ours! This exquisitely designed small bookcase from BEEUHLIL will help you please the bookworm in your life!This bookmark adopts an assembled triangle shape and is made of high-quality solid wood. It is small, exquisite, multi-functional and practical. Its design allows your favorite books to be kept at the last reading position. Of course, in addition to books, it can also be placed on mobile phones, tablets, and reading devices. The triangular interior can hold glasses, keys and other small items; the round bottom can hold some beverage cans, coffee cups, and red wine glasses; the pen holder can hold pencils and ballpoint pens that you usually use to record important parts of books.

reviews.reviewText: What a fun idea and perfect for your avid book reader like myself. I love that this little tray sits on your couch and can hold your coffee, book spot and pen while you get up. It is really cute as well to leave out and has a beautiful burnished design in the wood.The piece itself is made well and smooth. It comes almost assembled and just needs the two book holder wedges snapped together (they do easily) and add the silicone grips to the bottom of the tray so it doesn't move. Great gift idea as well!
